====================================
Prerequisite for upload
====================================

1. Server with ssh login should be available
2. All required packages on the server should be installed (nginx, php, mysql etc)
3. Cloudflare mapping to the domains / sub-domains should be done
4. Repositories and builds must be available to upload
    4.1 Repository of general source like APIs, Track, Cronjobs etc
    4.1 Working build of Web App
    4.2 Working build of Cross Platform Browser App
    4.3 Working build of Admin App
5. Stripe account for beta release customers data
6. Connect with the server and perform below mentioned steps


====================================
Create source code folders
====================================

$ sudo cd /var/www/html/saleshandy/

$ sudo mkdir v2

$ cd /var/www/html/saleshandy/v2/

$ sudo mkdir source

$ sudo mkdir web

$ sudo mkdir platform

$ sudo mkdir admin


====================================
Clone repositories
====================================

$ cd /var/www/html/saleshandy/v2/source/

$ git clone https://gitlab.com/saleshandy-app/core/webapp-v2.git .


$ cd /var/www/html/saleshandy/v2/web/

$ sudo wget <path-to-build-file>

$ sudo unzip -x <path-to-downloaded-file>

$ sudo mv dist public


$ cd /var/www/html/saleshandy/v2/platform/

$ sudo wget <path-to-build-file>

$ sudo unzip -x <path-to-downloaded-file>

$ sudo mv dist public


$ cd /var/www/html/saleshandy/v2/admin/

$ sudo wget <path-to-build-file>

$ sudo unzip -x <path-to-downloaded-file>

$ sudo mv dist public


====================================
Setup web application host file
====================================

Create host configuration file:
$ sudo nano /etc/nginx/sites-available/qa-web.saleshandy.com

Add following content:
server {
    listen 80;
    listen [::]:80;

    server_name qa-web.saleshandy.com;

    index index.html;

    error_log /var/log/nginx/qa-web-saleshandy-com-error.log;
    access_log /var/log/nginx/qa-web-saleshandy-com-access.log;

    root /var/www/html/saleshandy/v2/web/public;

    location / {
        try_files $uri $uri/ /index.html;
    }
}

Register virtual host with server configuration:
$ sudo ln -s /etc/nginx/sites-available/qa-web.saleshandy.com /etc/nginx/sites-enabled/


====================================
Setup APIs host file
====================================

Create host configuration file:
$ sudo nano /etc/nginx/sites-available/qa-api.saleshandy.com

Add following content:
server {
    listen 80;
    listen [::]:80;

    server_name qa-api.saleshandy.com;

    index api.php;

    error_log /var/log/nginx/qa-api-saleshandy-com-error.log;
    access_log /var/log/nginx/qa-api-saleshandy-com-access.log;

    root /var/www/html/saleshandy/v2/source/api;

    location / {
        try_files $uri /api.php$is_args$args;
    }

    location ~ \.php {
        try_files $uri =404;
        fastcgi_split_path_info ^(.+\.php)(/.+)$;
        fastcgi_pass unix:/var/run/php/php7.0-fpm.sock;

        include fastcgi_params;
        fastcgi_param SCRIPT_FILENAME $document_root$fastcgi_script_name;
        fastcgi_param SCRIPT_NAME $fastcgi_script_name;
        fastcgi_index api.php;
    }
}

Register virtual host with server configuration:
$ sudo ln -s /etc/nginx/sites-available/qa-api.saleshandy.com /etc/nginx/sites-enabled/


====================================
Setup document viewer host file
====================================

Create host configuration file:
$ sudo nano /etc/nginx/sites-available/qa-present.saleshandy.com

Add following content:
server {
    listen 80;
    listen [::]:80;

    server_name qa-present.saleshandy.com;

    index view.php;

    error_log /var/log/nginx/qa-present-saleshandy-com-error.log;
    access_log /var/log/nginx/qa-present-saleshandy-com-access.log;

    root /var/www/html/saleshandy/v2/source/docs;

    location / {
        try_files $uri /view.php$is_args$args;
    }

    location ~ \.php {
        try_files $uri =404;
        fastcgi_split_path_info ^(.+\.php)(/.+)$;
        fastcgi_pass unix:/var/run/php/php7.0-fpm.sock;

        include fastcgi_params;
        fastcgi_param SCRIPT_FILENAME $document_root$fastcgi_script_name;
        fastcgi_param SCRIPT_NAME $fastcgi_script_name;
        fastcgi_index view.php;
    }
}

Register virtual host with server configuration:
$ sudo ln -s /etc/nginx/sites-available/qa-present.saleshandy.com /etc/nginx/sites-enabled/


