====================================
Setup webhooks domain host files
====================================

Create host configuration file:
$ sudo nano /etc/nginx/sites-available/qa-wh.saleshandy.com

Add following content:
server {
    listen 80;
    listen [::]:80;

    server_name qa-wh.saleshandy.com;

    index incoming.php;

    error_log /var/log/nginx/qa-wh-saleshandy-com-error.log;
    access_log /var/log/nginx/qa-wh-saleshandy-com-access.log;

    root /var/www/html/saleshandy/v2/source/webhooks;

    location / {
        try_files $uri /incoming.php$is_args$args;
    }

    location ~ \.php {
        try_files $uri =404;
        fastcgi_split_path_info ^(.+\.php)(/.+)$;
        fastcgi_pass unix:/var/run/php/php7.0-fpm.sock;

        include fastcgi_params;
        fastcgi_param SCRIPT_FILENAME $document_root$fastcgi_script_name;
        fastcgi_param SCRIPT_NAME $fastcgi_script_name;
        fastcgi_index incoming.php;
    }
}

Register virtual host with server configuration:
$ sudo ln -s /etc/nginx/sites-available/qa-wh.saleshandy.com /etc/nginx/sites-enabled/


