====================================
Setup cross platform browser host file
====================================

Create host configuration file:
$ sudo nano /etc/nginx/sites-available/qa-platform.saleshandy.com

Add following content:
server {
    listen 80;
    listen [::]:80;

    server_name qa-platform.saleshandy.com;

    index index.html;

    error_log /var/log/nginx/platform-saleshandy-com-error.log;
    access_log /var/log/nginx/platform-saleshandy-com-access.log;

    root /var/www/html/saleshandy/v2/platform/public;

    location / {
        try_files $uri $uri/ /index.html;
    }
}

Register virtual host with server configuration:
$ sudo ln -s /etc/nginx/sites-available/qa-platform.saleshandy.com /etc/nginx/sites-enabled/


